'''''Kbela''''', ni filime ngufi yo muri Berezile 2015 iyobowe na Yasmin Thayna  ikorwa na Princeton yo muri Berezile LAB.   Filime yibanze ku ivanguramoko ryinjira mu buzima bw'abagore b'abirabura muri [[Burezile|Berezile]]. 

Filime yakiriwe neza kandi yegukana ibihembo byinshi mubirori mpuzamahanga bya firime.  Iyi filime yasohotse mu [[Buholandi]] ku ya 24 Mutarama 2019 mu Iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya firime Rotterdam . Ku ya 28 Ukwakira 2019, yasohotse mu iserukiramuco rya sinema rya  Carolina y'Amajyaruguru, muri [[Amerika]]. Muri 2017, iyi filime yahawe igihembo cyiza cya [[Afurika]] Diaspora Igihembo cya Afurika cyatanzwe na Africa Movie Academy Awards (AMAA).   

